N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4111.33 - Date of events

State Regulations

Before taking a nominating payment to an early closing
event, or any sustaining payment to a stake during the year the stake is to be
contested, the week and place of the race shall be announced and properly
advertised by the stake sponsor. Notes
